Pham into an attorney that is as comfortable acting as a drug crimes lawyer as he is taking on the role of a theft crime lawyer. The reason is simple: each of these roles, whether it is a DWI attorney, an assault attorney, a drug crime attorney, or a theft or burglary attorney, gives Pham the opportunity to come to the defense of those individuals who are wrongfully accused and who are facing down the strong-arm of the law. Working tirelessly on your case, The Law Office of Michael H. Pham goes the extra mile to improve the chances of a positive outcome in your case regardless of whether the charges against you are as simple as criminal mischief or as complicated as robbery. After all, even the simplest charges carry lasting consequences. No matter how challenging the case you’re involved in is, we’re excited to rise to the challenge of gathering evidence, crafting a defense, and battling it out in a court of law to prove your innocence. A criminal case is won by winning over a jury and to do that you need an attorney that cares about their clients. You need an attorney like Michael H. Pham that is willing to stick their neck out to defend you. Reach out to our law firm location in Houston to get started with a free consultation.

Description: Let's Gift It is a social gifting platform where individuals pool resources in order to purchase a gift.
Headquarters Regions: Greater New York Area, East Coast, Northeastern US
Full Description: Lets Gift It is an easy, fun and affordable way for friends, family, and coworkers to contribute towards the purchase of a gift for someone special. If you have ever organized or contributed towards a group gift, you know that collecting money, feeling obligated to give, and dealing with long email threads can be a pain. We experienced this pain and set out to build a better way to give as a group. Gift giving is about making someone's day special. Gift giving is not about how much you are able to spend. These two principals helped shape the product vision for Lets Gift It. We focused our efforts on creating a product that was easy to use, while making it affordable and fun for a folks who all have a connection to the recipient to give as a group. Lets Gift It is built on cutting edge technology to bring together people from a social graph, who for many different reasons, may not have otherwise been compelled to give a gift to a friend. Imagine its your birthday, and you opened the mail to find a new Callaway Driver generously gifted by the contributions of folks who may not know each other, but all know you. The collective buying power of the group can accomplish a lot of gifting.

Description: Company Description – Computer Aided Logistics Engineering, Inc. (CAL) is an established 22 year old biomedical technology company.
Headquarters Regions: Greater Miami Area, East Coast, Southern US
Full Description: Company Description – Computer Aided Logistics Engineering, Inc. (CAL) is an established 22 year old biomedical technology company headquartered in Ft. Lauderdale, FL. CAL has completed key projects in technological turn-key solutions for IBM, Motorola, Microsoft, Phillips, Coulter, Lucent and several other fortune 100 companies. In 1998, CAL spun off a program into the Dr. I-Net Corporation to automate medical records and reduce healthcare costs. In 2008, CAL developed DDM to address the unmet needs of obese and diabetic patients. CAL has completed the design and associated patents required by the US Patent and Trademark Office for the DDM. The DDM will be marketed to consumers directly, to be used in the comfort of their homes.
